Class Camioes

java.lang.Object
  Camioes

public class Camioes
extends java.lang.Object

The transport of the products is made by trucks which are characterized by an ID, a brand, a container, a position and have information about the kilometers traveled, kilometers traveled after the last inspection, number of inspections and if the container is placed or not.
